comment._content: I currently own Navion Nav-0401813.  Is this a picture of that specific serial number Navion?  Could this "Model 72" be my plane?? Ryan Navion 04-1813 is for sale on eBay NOW!

comment._content: [http://www.flickr.com/photos/71123110@N08] Sorry for the confusion! 04-01813 is our catalog number for the photo, not this navions registration number. A close up view of the N # on this navion is N4860K. Is this one yours: www.airport-data.com/aircraft/N4813K.html Thanks!

comment._content: Hello, My N number is like most Navions, the serial number plus 3000. My Serial number is NAV-04-1813 and my N number N-4813K. My log books are missing the first year, so I wondered if Ryan converted these Model 72's to GA aircraft. Quite a coincidense that your catalog numbers resemble the Navion serial number layout. Just sayin'. Thanks!
